features: [Traffic Scene Simulation] This classic cargo airplane toy included a traffic map, 6 construction trucks , a traffic light, 7 warning signs, etc. Various traffic signs are put on the traffic map, kids can obtain rich road traffic knowledge by playing car on the road of the map.

[Unique Features - Smoke Design] Compare with other planes, our airplane toy is larger （size：15.7''x14.9''x7.8''）, and increased simulated steam spray design. Just open the lid of the airplane, add to water, push it forward, and the tail of the airplane can produce a realistic spray effect.

[Large Airplane Toy with Two Slides] The airplane toy possesses a big cabin that can house 6 cars. two slide rails allow vehicles to slide out of the cabin, and a control button outside of the aircraft to control the cars slide forward or backward.

[Inertia Wheel Airplane with Light&Sound] Inertia glide design enables the aircraft to glide for a long distance on flat surfaces after a strong push. Pressing the 4 buttons above the cab makes different sounds effect and music. It has four lights and emits colorful flashing lights in the dark.3 AA batteries are required. (Not included)
[High Quality& Perfect Gift]-This airplane toy playset is made of environment-friendly ABS plastic material.A perfect gift for 3-12 years old boys girls for birthdays, Christmas, children's day, etc.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 24, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Surprisingly very good product
reviews.reviewText: I read the reviews for same product for other sellers who were selling it for or over $40. The reviews weren't great, but my Grandson specifically asked for a blue airplane. I ordered another type, but returned it because it was too small. When I received this airplane I was amazed at how great it was. It's not at all as big as pictured, but it was a good size and so easy to put together as it only had a few things to snap in. My Grandson loved it and it was only $32 from this seller. The cars were better quality than I expected and my Grandson loved the playmat!! Overall great toy!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Volume setting is way too loud
reviews.reviewText: Bought it for my soon to be 3 year old. The volume is way too loud and only comes in one setting. It is quite bulky and in order to shoot the cars out from either side, you really have to open the plane and balance the car in the middle on the table that tilts and shoot them one by one. Thinking of returning.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Low quality product picture misleading with size
reviews.reviewText: My son was so excited to open this as it was a gift. But unfortunately it broke within a day. He was heartbroken. I don’t recommend this product it’s verily cheaply made for the price, plus the wiring on the inside isn’t the safest for kids. Also the picture they use to get you to buy this item is very misleading as this plane is not that big.
